name: SoonChain
description: SoonChain is an AI-powered gaming L2, redefining game development with AIGG. SoonChain aims to revolutionize the gaming industry by leveraging AI to lower the barriers to entry for developers, making web3 accessible to a broader audience. We believe that everyone can be a developer, and with SoonChain, the true potential of web3 will be realized through a diverse and inclusive developer community.
